                        <head>No. 277.<lb/><hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Cushing</persName> to Mr. <persName type="to">Fish</persName>.</hi></head>
                        <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg></opener>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Madrid</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1875-08-23"><hi rend="italic">August</hi> 23,
                                1875</date>.</dateline></opener>
                        <p rend="center">* * * * * * *</p>
                        <p>Matter of Burriel is under discussion between minister of state and
                            myself. Copy of note and report of several personal interviews by
                            mail.</p>
                        <closer><signed>CUSHING.</signed></closer>
